Don't Just Manage — FlowSync\"** → Start Free Trial / Talk to Sales\n\n### HTML Worker — error\nERROR: No streaming chunk received for 120.0s (model=deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash, chunks_received=192). The connection may be alive at the TCP layer but is not producing content. Tune or disable via the `stream_chunk_timeout` constructor kwarg (set to None or 0 to disable) or the `LANGCHAIN_OPENAI_STREAM_CHUNK_TIMEOUT_S` env var. See also `http_socket_options` for the kernel-level TCP timeout that catches dead TCP peers.\n\n### CSS Worker — ok\n[frontend-css-b8fd2a37-89a2-4cf4-845a-51a832722e83] Exceeded max tool iterations (12)\n\n### JS Worker — ok\nThe file has been created and syntax-checked successfully. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ `main/script.js` — Interactive Enhancements\n\nThe script is wrapped in an IIFE with `'use strict'` and kicks off on `DOMContentLoaded`.\n\n### 1️⃣ Mobile Menu Toggle\n- Targets `.mobile-menu-toggle` and `.main-nav`\n- Toggles `aria-expanded` and adds `.main-nav--open` class\n- Closes on: link click, Escape key, click outside the header\n- Prevents body scroll while menu is open\n- Respects the CSS media query (menu hidden on desktop via `display: none`)\n\n### 2️⃣ Testimonial Carousel\n- Transforms the static `.testimonials-grid` into a carousel with tracking, prev/next buttons, and dot indicators\n- **Next/Previous buttons** with SVG arrow icons and `aria-label`\n- **Dot navigation** with `role=\"tablist\"` and `aria-selected` states\n- **Auto-advances** every 6 seconds; pauses on hover/focus\n- **Keyboard support**: ArrowLeft/ArrowRight, Escape not needed here\n- **Wrap-around** looping (infinite)\n- `aria-live=\"polite\"` on the track for screen reader announcements\n\n### 3️⃣ Smooth Scrolling\n- Event delegation on `document` for all `a[href^=\"#\"]` links\n- Prevents default, calculates offset based on sticky header height\n- Uses `window.scrollTo({ behavior: 'smooth' })`\n- Sets `tabindex=\"-1\"` + `focus